arances\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"world history\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American Sam Kendricks won his second Olympic medal, this time earning silver after clearing a season best of 5.95m.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999564102023261, \"rank\": 3.212201998197228e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Kendricks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his second Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"a season\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"5.95m.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze went to Greece's Emmanouil Karalis, who cleared 5.90m on his first jump.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999978802511307, \"rank\": 2.1197522110795673e-06, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanouil_Karalis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanouil Karalis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanouil_Karalis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanouil_Karalis\"}], \"noun_phr